data.title: Academic Achievement
data.meta_description: The MI faculty would like to congratulate the following students for achieving a place on the Dean’s List. We congratulate you on your academic achievement!
data.text:
THE DEAN’S LIST FOR MI’S SPRING 2024 QUARTER

The Senior Director, the Director of Performance Studies, and faculty at MI would like to congratulate the following students for achieving a place on the Dean’s List. The following students have completed a minimum of 12.0 units of letter-graded courses and have attained a Grade Point Average (GPA) of 3.7 or higher during the Spring 2024 Quarter.

We congratulate you on your academic achievement this past quarter and look forward to your continued success at Musicians Institute!

Thank you!
